  1. Community Voice is an open forum and dialog between the city and our citizens.

City Departments

  1. Building Inspections
    The Building Inspections Department is responsible for review of plans and issuance of building permits for all residential and commercial buildings and remodeling projects within the city. View Department
  2. Fire Department
    The City of Jesup Fire Department has 45 paid and volunteer personnel that serves both the City of Jesup and Wayne County.  View Department
  1. Downtown Development
    The Downtown Development Authority is committed to the economic development, historic preservation and beautification of Jesup's downtown area. View Department
  2. Police Department
    The mission of the Jesup Police Department is to strengthen and maintain the social order of the community by providing professional law enforcement services.  View Department
  1. Engineering Department
    The Engineering Department assists other departments in technical matters and problem solving necessary for them to meet the requirements of their department. View Department
  2. Public Works
    Public Works includes Sanitation, Streets, and Water. Find out what you can do to help keep the city in good shape.  View Department
